			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="option" style="--optionBackground:url(https://64.media.tumblr.com/36533e117af5c0ec13b5c0d0eb790986/c6e9191f31f3c156-2b/s400x600/5b562d346caeb20031fa229caf38c69a91265ccd.jpg);">
			<div class="shadow"></div>
			<div class="label">
				<div class="icon">
					<i class="fas fa-sun"></i>
